{"type":"message","id":"cab4c41e","parentId":"0f6ac98a","timestamp":"2026-03-14T15:17:52.608Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"噫！君子何事臨軒，欲破殼而出乎？抑或有他求於區區？吾雖微賤，亦當竭誠以助。請道其詳，毋隱毋匿。"}],"api":"mistral-conversations","provider":"mistral","model":"mistral-large-latest","usage":{"input":1152,"output":63,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":1215,"cost":{"input":0.000576,"output":0.0000945,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0006705}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773501469995}}
