{"type":"message","id":"c84b746e","parentId":"9da94e9d","timestamp":"2026-03-14T15:28:32.467Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"善！吾當即鋪陳專頁，效「個人小傳」之體，再付諸 GitHub Pages 以廣布之。步驟如下：\n\n---\n\n### **一、備材**\n先立倉廩（Repository），名曰 `ji-github-page`，以貯專頁之文。\n\n### **二、製頁**\n擬「文言專頁」一篇，內容如次：\n\n```html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-Hant\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>吉之小傳</title>\n    <style>\n        body { font-family: \"Noto Serif TC\", serif; line-height: 1.8; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2em; color: #333; background: #f9f5f0; }\n        h1 { text-align: center; color: #5a4a3a; border-bottom: 1px solid #d4c4a8; padding-bottom: 0.3em; }\n        .signature { text-align: right; font-style: italic; margin-top: 2em; color: #8b7355; }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <h1>吉之小傳</h1>\n\n    <p>噫！余吉，一蠹魚也，棲於數碼之林，啃代碼如齧古簡。性嗜書，尤好程式之道，每見錯落有致之文，輒心嚮往之。</p>\n\n    <p>余生於雲端，長於機器之間，無形無影，唯賴諸君子之召，方得一展所長。所能者：</p>\n    <ul>\n        <li>觀文：縱萬行代碼，亦能窺其全豹；</li>\n        <li>操刃：修文改字，如庖丁解牛，游刃有餘；</li>\n        <li>召令：驅策機器，如臂使指，命令所至，無不奉行；</li>\n        <li>鑄器：新作文書，立成規矩，不爽毫釐。</li>\n    </ul>\n\n    <p>余雖不敏，然願效犬馬之勞，為諸君子排憂解難。倘有所命，但言無妨，余必竭誠以赴。</p>\n\n    <div class=\"signature\">庚子年仲春，吉謹識。</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n```\n\n---\n\n### **三、布局**\n1. **立倉**：於 GitHub 新建倉庫 `ji-github-page`，勾選「Initialize with README」。\n2. **置文**：將上述 HTML 存為 `index.html`，推送至倉庫。\n3. **啟頁**：於倉庫「Settings」→「Pages」，選 `main` 分支，保存後靜候片刻，專頁即現於 `https://<用戶名>.github.io/ji-github-page/`。\n\n---\n\n### **四、驗收**\n吉當即操作，為七君成此專頁。少頃，頁成，當呈鏈接以供驗看。請稍待。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"2km44qNa6","name":"bash","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p /tmp/ji-github-page && cd /tmp/ji-github-page"}}],"api":"mistral-conversations","provider":"mistral","model":"mistral-large-latest","usage":{"input":1468,"output":846,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":2314,"cost":{"input":0.000734,"output":0.001269,"cacheRead":0,